# =============================================================================
# ENVIRONMENT NOTES
# =============================================================================
# 
# DEVELOPMENT (.env):
# - Use local services (localhost URLs)
# - Enable debug features
# - Use weak security (faster development)
# - Enable hot reload
#
# STAGING (.env.staging):
# - Use staging services
# - Enable some debug features
# - Use medium security
# - Test production-like behavior
#
# PRODUCTION (.env.production):
# - Use production services
# - Disable debug features  
# - Use strong security
# - Optimize for performance
# - Never expose secrets in build
#
# =============================================================================